# Local MCP client config — Claude Code reads `.mcp.json` at the
# repo root for project-scoped MCP server connections. Per-contributor;
# typically contains auth tokens (e.g. Penpot MCP). Never commit.
# A redacted `.mcp.json.example` may be committed as a template.
.mcp.json

# Runtime
.turbo/

# Wrangler local state — Miniflare D1/KV/R2/Queues volumes generated
# by `wrangler pages dev` and `wrangler d1 ... --local`. Per-contributor,
# never committed.
.wrangler/
.dev.vars
.dev.vars.local
# Vite reads `.env.local` at the repo root (envDir override in
# vite.config.ts). Per-developer values; never committed.
.env.local
.env.*.local
# Output of `npm run gen:node-key`; the wire-format public key is
# also persisted in node_identity.public_key, so this file is just
# a convenience for paste-into-portal flows.
node-public-key.txt

# Test / coverage artifacts
coverage/
